      <title>基于butterfly主题的markdown使用教程及示例</title>
      <link href="/2022/12/10/markdown2/"/>
      <url>/2022/12/10/markdown2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这篇文章是用来记录markdown的使用方式，几乎包含了所有markdown的用法。</p><hr><h1 id="1-标题"><a href="#1-标题" class="headerlink" title="1.标题"></a>1.标题</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># H1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## H2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### H3</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#### H4</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">##### H5</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">###### H6</span></span><br><span class="line">或者，对于H1和H2，使用下划线样式:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">Alt-H1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">======</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">Alt-H2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">------</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="H1"><a href="#H1" class="headerlink" title="H1"></a>H1</h1><h2 id="H2"><a href="#H2" class="headerlink" title="H2"></a>H2</h2><h3 id="H3"><a href="#H3" class="headerlink" title="H3"></a>H3</h3><h4 id="H4"><a href="#H4" class="headerlink" title="H4"></a>H4</h4><h5 id="H5"><a href="#H5" class="headerlink" title="H5"></a>H5</h5><h6 id="H6"><a href="#H6" class="headerlink" title="H6"></a>H6</h6><h1 id="Alt-H1"><a href="#Alt-H1" class="headerlink" title="Alt-H1"></a>Alt-H1</h1><h2 id="Alt-H2"><a href="#Alt-H2" class="headerlink" title="Alt-H2"></a>Alt-H2</h2><hr><h1 id="2-强调词句（斜体、粗体、删除线）"><a href="#2-强调词句（斜体、粗体、删除线）" class="headerlink" title="2.强调词句（斜体、粗体、删除线）"></a>2.强调词句（斜体、粗体、删除线）</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">斜体，使用<span class="emphasis">*星号*</span>或者<span class="emphasis">_下划线_</span>。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">加粗，使用<span class="strong">**两个星号**</span>或者<span class="strong">__两个下划线__</span>.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">同时使用，使用<span class="strong">**星号和<span class="emphasis">_下划线_</span>**</span>.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">删除线使用两个波浪号. ~~像这样~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>斜体，使用<em>星号</em>或者_下划线_。</p><p>加粗，使用<strong>两个星号</strong>或者__两个下划线__.</p><p>同时使用，使用<strong>星号和_下划线_</strong>.</p><p>删除线使用两个波浪号. <del>像这样</del></p><hr><h1 id="3-序号"><a href="#3-序号" class="headerlink" title="3.序号"></a>3.序号</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 第一个有序列表项</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 另一个项目</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="emphasis">*无序子列表。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">1. 实际的数字不重要，它只是一个数字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">  1. 命令列表</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">4. 还有一项。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">   您可以在列表项中适当地缩进段落。注意上面的空行和前导空格(至少一个，但我们在这里将使用三个空格来对齐原始Markdown)。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*</span> 无序列表可以使用星号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 或减号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">+</span> 或加号</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 段落无序列表</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  比如这样。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">带有一些文本的公共段落。</span><br><span class="line">还有更多的文字。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol><li>第一个有序列表项</li><li>另一个项目</li></ol><ul><li>无序子列表。</li></ul><ol><li><p>实际的数字不重要，它只是一个数字</p></li><li><p>命令列表</p></li><li><p>还有一项。</p><p>您可以在列表项中适当地缩进段落。注意上面的空行和前导空格(至少一个，但我们在这里将使用三个空格来对齐原始Markdown)。</p></li></ol><ul><li>无序列表可以使用星号</li></ul><ul><li>或减号</li></ul><ul><li>或加号</li></ul><ul><li><p>段落无序列表</p><p>比如这样。</p></li></ul><p>带有一些文本的公共段落。<br>还有更多的文字。</p><hr><h1 id="4-HTML内链"><a href="#4-HTML内链" class="headerlink" title="4.HTML内链"></a>4.HTML内链</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span>重新启动计算机，按<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">kbd</span>&gt;</span></span>ctrl<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">kbd</span>&gt;</span></span>+<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">kbd</span>&gt;</span></span>alt<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">kbd</span>&gt;</span></span>+<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">kbd</span>&gt;</span></span>del<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">kbd</span>&gt;</span></span>.<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重新启动计算机，按<kbd>ctrl</kbd>+<kbd>alt</kbd>+<kbd>del</kbd>.</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;dt&gt;定义列表&lt;/dt&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;dd&gt;人们有时会用到的东西&lt;/dd&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;dt&gt;Markdown in HTML&lt;/dt&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;dd&gt;Does *not* work **very** well. Use HTML &lt;em&gt;tags&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/dd&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&lt;/dl&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><dl>    <dt>定义列表</dt>    <dd>人们有时会用到的东西</dd><pre><code>&lt;dt&gt;Markdown in HTML&lt;/dt&gt;&lt;dd&gt;Does *not* work **very** well. Use HTML &lt;em&gt;tags&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/dd&gt;</code></pre></dl><hr><h1 id="5-链接"><a href="#5-链接" class="headerlink" title="5.链接"></a>5.链接</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">我是一个内链风格的链接</span>](<span class="link">https://hexo.io</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">我是一个内链风格的标题链接</span>](<span class="link">https://hexo.io &quot;hexo主页&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">我是一个参考风格的链接</span>][<span class="symbol">任意文本</span>]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">我是存储库文件的相对引用</span>](<span class="link">../blob/master/LICENSE</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">可以在引用样式的链接定义中使用数字</span>][<span class="symbol">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">或者留空，使用 [链接文本本身]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">一些文本显示的参考链接可以写在后面。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">任意文本</span>]: <span class="link">https://hexo.io</span></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">1</span>]: <span class="link">https://hexo.io/docs/</span></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">链接文本本身</span>]: <span class="link">https://hexo.io/api/</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://www.bilibili.com/&quot;</span> <span class="attr">target</span>=<span class="string">&quot;_blank&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;https://yhmyhm.cn/img/dm1.webp&quot;</span> <span class="attr">alt</span>=<span class="string">&quot;我是一个图片链接&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;240&quot;</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">&quot;180&quot;</span> <span class="attr">border</span>=<span class="string">&quot;10&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">![我是一个图片链接</span>](<span class="link">https://yhmyhm.cn/img/dm1.webp</span>)](<span class="link">https://www.bilibili.com/</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><a href="https://hexo.io/">我是一个内链风格的链接</a></p><p><a href="https://hexo.io/" title="hexo主页">我是一个内链风格的标题链接</a></p><p><a href="https://hexo.io/">我是一个参考风格的链接</a></p><p><a href="../blob/master/LICENSE">我是存储库文件的相对引用</a></p><p><a href="https://hexo.io/docs/">可以在引用样式的链接定义中使用数字</a></p><p>或者留空，使用 <a href="https://hexo.io/api/">链接文本本身</a></p><p>一些文本显示的参考链接可以写在后面。</p><p>可以通过修改参数来控制图片修改、图片大小、链接指向。</p><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/" target="_blank"><img src="https://yhmyhm.cn/img/dm1.webp" alt="我是一个图片链接" width="240" height="180" border="10" /></a></p><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/"><img src="https://yhmyhm.cn/img/dm1.webp" alt="我是一个图片链接"></a></p><hr><h1 id="6-图片"><a href="#6-图片" class="headerlink" title="6.图片"></a>6.图片</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">悬停查看标题文本：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">内链样式：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">alt text</span>](<span class="link">https://hexo.io/icon/favicon-196x196.png &quot;标志文本1&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">参考格式：</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">alt text</span>][<span class="symbol">logo</span>]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="symbol">logo</span>]: <span class="link">https://hexo.io/icon/favicon-196x196.png &quot;标志文本2&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>悬停查看标题文本：</p><p>内链样式：</p><p><img src="https://hexo.io/icon/favicon-196x196.png" alt="alt text" title="标志文本1"></p><p>参考格式：</p><p><img src="https://hexo.io/icon/favicon-196x196.png" alt="alt text" title="标志文本2"></p><hr><h1 id="7-代码"><a href="#7-代码" class="headerlink" title="7.代码"></a>7.代码</h1><p>内联代码前后有三个独立成行的反引号,在开头的三个反引号后面加上语言类型即可定义语言（注意不要换行），例如：JavaScript、Python、MARKDOWN等。</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> s = <span class="string">&quot;JavaScript syntax highlighting&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_">alert</span>(s);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">s = <span class="string">&quot;Python syntax highlighting&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span> s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">No language indicated, so no syntax highlighting.</span><br><span class="line">But let&#x27;s throw in a &lt;b&gt;tag&lt;/b&gt;.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="8-表格"><a href="#8-表格" class="headerlink" title="8.表格"></a>8.表格</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">|                |ASCII                          |HTML                         |</span><br><span class="line">|----------------|-------------------------------|-----------------------------|</span><br><span class="line">|Single backticks|<span class="code">`&#x27;Isn&#x27;t this fun?&#x27;`</span>            |&#x27;Isn&#x27;t this fun?&#x27;            |</span><br><span class="line">|Quotes          |<span class="code">`&quot;Isn&#x27;t this fun?&quot;`</span>            |&quot;Isn&#x27;t this fun?&quot;            |</span><br><span class="line">|Dashes          |<span class="code">`-- is en-dash, --- is em-dash`</span>|-- is en-dash, --- is em-dash|</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th></th><th>ASCII</th><th>HTML</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Single backticks</td><td><code>&#39;Isn&#39;t this fun?&#39;</code></td><td>‘Isn’t this fun?’</td></tr><tr><td>Quotes</td><td><code>&quot;Isn&#39;t this fun?&quot;</code></td><td>“Isn’t this fun?”</td></tr><tr><td>Dashes</td><td><code>-- is en-dash, --- is em-dash</code></td><td>– is en-dash, — is em-dash</td></tr></tbody></table><p>冒号可用于列对齐，不使用为左对齐，前后均使用为居中对齐，后面使用为右对齐。</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| Tables        | Are           | Cool  |</span><br><span class="line">| ------------- |:-------------:| -----:|</span><br><span class="line">| col 3 is      | right-aligned |  |</span><br><span class="line">| col 2 is      | centered      |    |</span><br><span class="line">| zebra stripes | are neat      |   </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th>Tables</th><th align="center">Are</th><th align="right">Cool</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>col 3 is</td><td align="center">right-aligned</td><td align="right"></td></tr><tr><td>col 2 is</td><td align="center">centered</td><td align="right"></td></tr><tr><td>zebra stripes</td><td align="center">are neat</td><td align="right"></td></tr></tbody></table><p>最外层的(|)可以不需要，也不需要使用空格使原始Markdown行列对齐，同时也可以在表格内使用Markdown。</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Markdown | Less | Pretty</span><br><span class="line">--- | --- | ---</span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*Still*</span> | <span class="code">`renders`</span> | <span class="strong">**nicely**</span></span><br><span class="line">1 | 2 | 3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th>Markdown</th><th>Less</th><th>Pretty</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><em>Still</em></td><td><code>renders</code></td><td><strong>nicely</strong></td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td>2</td><td>3</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h1 id="9-块引用"><a href="#9-块引用" class="headerlink" title="9.块引用"></a>9.块引用</h1><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;blockquote&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;这里的文字不限字数，并且可以把Markdown写进来&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/blockquote&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>这里的文字不限字数，并且可以把Markdown写进来</p></blockquote><hr><h1 id="10-分割线"><a href="#10-分割线" class="headerlink" title="10.分割线"></a>10.分割线</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">连字符</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">***</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">星号</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">___</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">下划线</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><p>连字符</p><hr><p>星号</p><hr><p>下划线</p><hr><h1 id="11-换行符"><a href="#11-换行符" class="headerlink" title="11.换行符"></a>11.换行符</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是一段开场白。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这一行与上面的一行用两个换行符隔开，因此它将是一个单独的段落。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这一行也是一个单独的段落，但是……</span><br><span class="line">这一行仅由单个换行符分隔，因此它是同一段中的独立行。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这是一段开场白。</p><p>这一行与上面的一行用两个换行符隔开，因此它将是一个单独的段落。</p><p>这一行也是一个单独的段落，但是……<br>这一行仅由单个换行符分隔，因此它是同一段中的独立行。</p><hr><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是一个段落。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;tr&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">        &lt;td&gt;Hi&lt;/td&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;/tr&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&lt;/table&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line">这是另一个段落。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这是一个段落。</p><table>    <tr>        <td>Hi</td>    </tr></table><p>这是另一个段落。</p><hr>]]></content>
      
      
